---
title: Creamy Dijon Mushroom Chicken Breast Stew with Smashed Potatoes
description: In this luxurious stew, chicken and mushrooms simmer away in a tangy, rosemary-kissed, Dijon cream sauce. Smashed potatoes are just the side you need to soak up the rich flavours. This meal will bring a taste of France to your table any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-cremeux-de-poitrines-de-poulet-et-de-champignons-a-la-dijonnaise-47fa7a11.jpg
